title: The American Dream Attained: An Interview with Ed Moy
itunes:title: The American Dream Attained: An Interview with Ed Moy
description: Ed Moy began as a child of immigrant parents from China and advanced all the way to the White House as President George W. Bush’s Special Assistant to the President for Presidential Personnel from 2001-2006.  He was then appointed as the 38th Director of the U.S. Mint from 2006-2011.
